translations.stoller_miller:
Perform necessary action;
it is more powerful than inaction;
without action you even fail
to sustain your own body.

translations.gemini:
Beings come into existence from food; 
 the production of food is from rain (parjanya). 
 Rain comes into existence from sacrifice (yajña); 
 sacrifice is born of action (karma).

translations.stoller_miller:
Even a man of knowledge
behaves in accord with his own nature;
creatures all conform to nature;
what can one do to restrain them?

translations.gemini:
They say the senses are supreme; 
 beyond the senses is the mind; 
 Beyond the mind is the understanding (buddhi); 
 but what is beyond the understanding (buddhi), that is He.
